# CODEOWNERS — requested reviewers for every PR.
# Replace @YOUR_GITHUB_HANDLE with the maintainer's username (or @org/team).
# Branch protection requires review from a code owner; the ruleset grants the
# owner a bypass so a solo maintainer is not deadlocked on their own PRs.
# Owning /.github/ here means a PR cannot rewrite its own reviewers or workflows.
*                @YOUR_GITHUB_HANDLE
/.github/        @YOUR_GITHUB_HANDLE
